India Bonds Gain as RBI Says Interest-Rate Increases Nearing End

-- B y   V   R a m a k r i s h n a n
-- 
2011-09-23T03:41:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/india-bonds-gain-as-rbi-says-interest-rate-increases-nearing-end.html
India ’s 10-year bonds advanced a
third day after the Reserve Bank of India Deputy Governor  Subir
Gokarn  said the central bank is close to the end of interest-
rate increases.  The yield on the 7.80 percent note due April 2021 fell one
basis point to 8.29 percent as of 9:08 a.m. in Mumbai, according
to the central bank’s trading system.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
V Ramakrishnan at 
 rvenkatarama@bloomberg.net  